<main class="project">
    <div class="project-details">
        <div class="project-desc">
            <h1 id="project-text"><span id="ani1">Welcome to the Online Budget Tracker!.</span>Our goal is to empower you with tools
                to monitor and <span id="ani2">control your expenses</span> effectively, helping you to <span id="ani3"> cut unnecessary spending </span>and save
                for what truly matters.</h1>
            <div class="project-metadata">
                <div class="box one">
                    <h2>Objective</h2>
                    <ul id="project-obj">
                        <li>Reduce unnecessary spending.</li>
                        <li>Provide actionable insights into your financial habits.</li>
                        <li>Help you set and achieve savings goals.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="box two">
                    <h2>Features</h2>
                    <ul id="project-features">
                        <li >
                            <h3>Expense Management</h3>
                            <ol class="inner-list">
                                <li>Add, edit, and delete expenses.</li>
                                <li>Categorize expenses as essential or non-essential.</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li >
                            <h3>Budget Tracking</h3>
                            <ol class="inner-list">
                                <li>Set monthly or yearly budgets.</li>
                                <li>Get alerts when you're close to exceeding your budget.</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <h3>Data Visualization</h3>
                            <ol  class="inner-list">
                                <li>View spending trends through pie charts, bar graphs, and line charts.</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-steps">
            <h2>Steps to follow</h2>
            <ul id="project-features">
                <li>
                <h3>Step 1: Register your account</h3>
                  <ul class="inner-list">
                    <li>Visit the registration page.</li>
                    <li>Enter your details (name, email, password).</li>
                    <li>Click on the 'Register' button to create your account.</li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Step 2: Log in with your account</h3>
                  <ul class="inner-list">
                    <li>Go to the login page.</li>
                    <li>Enter your registered email and password.</li>
                    <li>Click on the 'Login' button to access your account.</li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Step 3: Enter your budget in Budget Buddy</h3>
                  <ul class="inner-list">
                    <li>Go to the 'Budget Buddy' section.</li>
                    <li>Enter the amount you want to set for your budget.</li>
                    <li>Click on the 'Save Budget' button to store your budget.</li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Step 4: Enter your spendings in the current budget page</h3>
                  <ul class="inner-list">
                    <li>Navigate to the 'Current Budget' page.</li>
                    <li>Input your spending details (e.g., amount, category, date).</li>
                    <li>Click on 'Add Spending' to record the transaction.</li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Step 5: View past budgets in the 'Past Budgets' page</h3>
                  <ul class="inner-list">
                    <li>Go to the 'Past Budgets' section.</li>
                    <li>Browse through your previously saved budgets.</li>
                    <li>Select a past budget to view its details.</li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
              </ul>
              
        </div>
    </div>
